\pi1 (Scriptures) \xt Matiu 4:1-4; 5:17-20; 22:29; Jon 8:31-32; 20:31; Buka Tatau'aro 20:32; Rom 15:4; 16:26; Kolosae 3:16; 1 Tesalonaeka 2:13; 1 Timoti 4:13; 2 Timoti 3:14-17; Hibru 4:12; 1 Pita 1:22-25; 2 Pita 1:19-21; 2 Jon 9-10; Buka Ha'ata'i 1:3. \xt*
\p \k Waiai nata sae na'i kooti\k*
